                    {{!-- term and condition modal --}}
                    <div class="modal fade" id="term" aria-hidden="true" data-bs-backdrop="true">
                        <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
                            <div class="modal-content">
                                <!-- head -->
                                <div class="modal-header align-items-center">
                                    <h5 style="color:red; font-family: Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;"
                                        class="text-center w-100 m-0" id="exampleModalLabel">
                                        Term and Condition
                                    </h5>
                                    <button id="btncloseterm" type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"
                                        aria-label="Close"></button>
                                </div>

                                <p
                                    style=" word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 600px; padding-left:10px; padding-right:10px;">
                                    Collect idea system is a platform that provides universities and organizations with
                                    a centralized location for collecting, managing, and evaluating ideas from
                                    employees.
                                    The platform allows users to create customizable idea submission forms, and
                                    communicate with idea submitters throughout the process.
                                </p>
                                <p
                                    style=" word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 600px; padding-left:10px">
                                    When you submit an idea, you have to agree to the following terms and conditions:
                                    <li style="padding-left:10px">
                                        Ideas must be original.
                                    </li>
                                    <li style="padding-left:10px">
                                        Ideas must not be confidential.
                                    </li>
                                    <li style="padding-left:10px">
                                        Ideas must be relevant.
                                    </li>
                                    <li style="padding-left:10px">
                                        Ideas must be actionable.
                                    </li>
                                </p>
                                <p
                                    style=" word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 600px; padding-left:10px; padding-right:10px;">
                                    Overall, the collect idea system offers a comprehensive solution for managing the
                                    ideation process within an organization. However, users must carefully review and
                                    adhere to the platform's terms and conditions to ensure that they are using the
                                    platform in a responsible and compliant manner.
                                </p>

                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <hr />
                    <!-- actions -->
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-lg-row mt-3">
